WEBVTT

00:00:01.372 --> 00:00:05.460
If I asked you to guess
which country in the world

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:08.713
has the highest number
of female entrepreneurs,

00:00:10.089 --> 00:00:11.966
which country would you guess?

00:00:12.008 --> 00:00:13.801
Don't worry. I'll tell you.

00:00:13.843 --> 00:00:14.927
(Laughter)

00:00:14.969 --> 00:00:19.849
Uganda, yup, in Africa.

00:00:19.891 --> 00:00:22.977
39.6 of all Ugandans

00:00:22.977 --> 00:00:27.482
who start, own and operate
their own businesses are women.

00:00:28.357 --> 00:00:32.403
Ugandan women are clearly formidable,
but they are not alone.